| Module | Path | Responsibility | Notes |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Backend Core Config | `Huz-Backend/huz` | Django settings, root URL routing, ASGI/WSGI bootstrapping | Root URL includes `/api/v1`, `/common`, `/partner`, `/bookings`, `/management`, `/chat` |
| Common Domain | `Huz-Backend/common` | End-user auth/profile, OTP, address, firebase token, user wallet/account primitives | 17 backend endpoints; 10 currently consumed by FE |
| Partner Domain | `Huz-Backend/partners` | Partner auth/profile, package lifecycle, website listing APIs, partner wallet ops | 37 backend endpoints; 36 consumed by FE |
| Booking Domain | `Huz-Backend/booking` | Booking creation/payment/passport, partner booking operations, complaints/reviews/requests | 34 legacy booking endpoints; 31 consumed by FE; shared traveler-count helper now lives in `booking/flow_utils.py` for reuse from `services.py` and `management/approval_task.py` |
| Booking v1 API | `Huz-Backend/booking/api_urls.py`, `Huz-Backend/booking/views/api_v1.py` | DRF booking endpoints under `/api/v1` | 5 v1 endpoints; 3 consumed by FE |
| Management Domain | `Huz-Backend/management` | Super-admin approvals, payment transfer, reporting/KPI, hotel master catalog | 24 endpoints; 9 consumed by FE |
| Chat Domain | `Huz-Backend/chat` | REST chat inbox/message endpoints + websocket routing | 5 REST endpoints; 0 consumed by current FE API literals |
| Web App Shell | `Huz-Web-Frontend/src` | Public site, booking flow, user settings UI | Routing in `src/routes/AppRoutes.jsx`; current route tree exposes 43 routes (`28` public/auth, `12` canonical protected, `3` protected aliases) |
| Web Shared Layout System | `Huz-Web-Frontend/src/shared/layout`, `Huz-Web-Frontend/src/pages/HomePage/homepageLayout.js`, `Huz-Web-Frontend/src/styles/globals.css` | Shared shell, width/rhythm tokens, branded surfaces, ambient background contract | Primary page-system contract for the revamp; used by Home, Listing, Package Detail, Hajj Guidance, Booking, Payment Methods, Personal Details, and AuthLayout |
| Web Static Content System | `Huz-Web-Frontend/src/features/staticPages`, `Huz-Web-Frontend/src/features/staticPages/content` | Shared branded content shell plus route-driven content modules for public info/legal pages | Powers `HowWeWork`, `AboutUs`, `CoreValues`, `ComingSoon`, `FrequentlyAskedQuestions`, `PolicyPages`, `GenericPages`, `PrivacyPolicy`, and `TermsServices`; this earlier public/static batch remains verified, and the lead-gen routes are now the remaining public pages still outside the shared branded systems |
| Web Pilgrimage Guide System | `Huz-Web-Frontend/src/features/pilgrimageGuides`, `Huz-Web-Frontend/src/features/pilgrimageGuides/content` | Shared branded guide/article and holy-site city templates plus route-content modules | Powers `PreparationTips`, `TravelEssentials`, `UmrahGuide`, `MakkahHolySites`, `MadinahHolySites`, `JeddahHolySites`, and `TaifHolySites`; centralizes `BrandPageShell`, routed `CityNavbar`, related-article cards, `react-slick` settings, and shared promo placement |
| Web Guide and Holy-Site Pages | `Huz-Web-Frontend/src/pages/PreparationTips`, `TravelEssentials`, `UmrahGuide`, `MakkahHolySites`, `MadinahHolySites`, `JeddahHolySites`, `TaifHolySites` | Route-owner wrappers for pilgrimage content pages | The 7 route files are now thin wrappers over the shared pilgrimage guide system, so the duplicated `Header`/`Footer`, hero, related-article, and city-carousel layout logic no longer lives in each route owner |
| Web Lead and Partner Pages | `Huz-Web-Frontend/src/pages/VisaServices`, `ContactUs`, `HajjUmrahBusiness`, `ListPackagePage` | Acquisition, contact, and partner-onboarding routes now aligned to shared static/marketing systems | `VisaServices` and `ContactUs` now persist browser-local lead drafts via `features/marketingPages/leadCaptureDrafts.js` (no API calls), `HajjUmrahBusiness` keeps intentional CTA routing to `/list-your-packages` and `operator.hajjumrah.co`, and `ListPackagePage` preserves intentional outbound operator links |
| Web Auth Surface | `Huz-Web-Frontend/src/features/auth`, `Huz-Web-Frontend/src/pages/Login`, `Huz-Web-Frontend/src/pages/Signup`, `Huz-Web-Frontend/src/pages/Otp` | OTP-driven traveler signup/login/verification flow | All auth routes now funnel through `AuthLayout` |
